Package: randbn
Type: Package
Title: Simulate bayesian networks
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Vera Kvisgaard
Maintainer: The package maintainer <verakvisgaard@gmail.com>
Description: The package includes simple routines for simulating bayesian networks, 
   that is DAGs and local distributions. These are compatible with the bn.fit class of the bnlearn package.
